                  <summary change="#add-summary">
                     A Persian-Turkish <title>Lughat</title> (Dictionary) by <persName key="person_296599726" ref="https://viaf.org/viaf/296599726/">Niʻmat Allāh Rūmī (d. 1562)</persName>. 
