                        bin el-Mevlā el-Merḥūm Meḥmed el-Kördüsī</persName> on <date calendar="#Hijri-qamari" when="1714-09-15">6 Ramaz̤ān 1126 AH (15 Sept. 1714 CE)</date>.                  
                  </summary>
