                     <supportDesc material="chart">
                        <support>Textblock of cross-grained, ivoury-coloured <material>paper</material> probably handmade in the <placeName cert="high" ref="http://vocab.getty.edu/page/tgn/7000208" key="place_7000208">Indian subcontinent</placeName> with ~8 laid lines per cm and no discernible chain lines.</support>
                        <extent>
