                        </extent>
                        <foliation xml:id="modern">Foliated with modern pencilled Arabic numerals on the upper-left corners of the a sides throughout, referenced in this record.</foliation>
                        <foliation xml:id="original">Hindu-Arabic numerals on the upper-left corners of the a sides, inclusive of the flyleaves.</foliation>
                        <collation> Undetermined. <catchwords>Catchwords throughout most of the lower-left corners of the b sides.</catchwords></collation>
                        <condition>In fair condition, with moderate water and insect damage and historical repairs throughout.</condition>
                     </supportDesc>
                     <layoutDesc>
                        <layout columns="1" ruledLines="27" n="mistara">  Written in 1 column with 27 lines per page. Ruled with a <hi rend="italic">misṭarah</hi> hand guide.</layout>                  
                     </layoutDesc>
